race.description: Catalano Sales And Hire Navy Cup Mbl Pace (G3)
race.comment: MAGNIFICENT STORM NZ (4) has had tough draws and has only been about 3.5m from a couple of topliners at his last two outings. Had won three in a row at this circuit prior. He looks very hard to stop from this lower draw. PENNY BLACK NZ (11) was held up when midfield last week. Had been in terrific form with a string of top-two finishes prior. Can get into the finish with even luck from the back row. LITTLE DARLING (12) made it back-to-back wins when beating Penny Black in the G1 Westral Classic here last start. Cops a second row draw this time but winning form is hard to knock. LAVRA JOE (2) has come from wider barriers at his last couple of outings. Building in fitness and draws to advantage.
